import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['age'] = pd.to_numeric(data['age'], errors='coerce')
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='age', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['age'].median(), color='red', label='Median Age: {:.2f}'.format(data['age'].median()))
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the age distribution of the deceased?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
